    "sector_hint": "Food & Beverage",
    "dialect_hint": null,
    "color_palette": "Crimson oxblood red (~#9E1B1B) as the dominant brand color, with warm gold (~#C9971F) as the partner accent and cream (~#F3EAD7) as the neutral ground. Red leads (it is the gift-box and the badge); gold signs the wordmark/lid; cream carries the food and copy. · Warm, dark-leaning heritage ground — deep saturated heritage textile (red tribal/Persian carpet or Najdi sadu weave) under warm low-key directional light, OR a clean warm cream studio sweep for CTA/packaging beauty shots. Never cool, never pure-white clinical, never daylight-flat. Shadows are warm and present (chiaroscuro), not lifted.",
    "style_descriptor": "Warm, intimate, appetite-first food photography with a documentary-Najdi-home feel: a single warm directional key (golden/tungsten), shallow depth-of-field isolating the dish, visible steam, glistening samn/oil pooling on the porridge surface, real plated heat — staged on authentic heritage surfaces (sadu weave, tribal carpet, palm-frond mat, clay finjan). Soft-edged shadows, not hard studio editorial; the 'just-served at the family table' character, never sterile pack-shot.",
    "lighting": null,
    "people_in_frame": "none",
    "filter_style": null,
    "style_register": null,
    "identity_dna": "A thick, creamy off-white cracked-wheat porridge, slow-cooked to a smooth oatmeal-like consistency and glistening with a pour of dark amber ghee (سمن). It is crowned with a vivid scarlet roasted-pepper-and-tomato salsa and whole red chilies, served either in a single white kraft cup or a round family-size aluminum-foil tray nested in the brand's signature red box.",
    "color_field_palette": "Three brand-owned fields ONLY, all evidenced from the real packaging/identity: (1) deep crimson oxblood red (the signature gift-box red) ~#9E1B1B–#7E1414; (2) warm gold / mustard-yellow (the eight-point-star lid label + gold serving pot + 'أطلب الان' CTA) ~#C9971F–#E0B23A; (3) cream / ivory off-white (the kraft cup body + star-label field + lower CTA band) ~#F3EAD7. A color-blocking chain fills the frame with crimson, gold, or cream — and pops via their mutual contrast (crimson↔cream, gold↔crimson). EXCLUDE: blue, the carpet's indigo, terracotta-as-field (terracotta is a companion/apron color, not a fill field), and any borrowed reference red/orange.",
    "material_texture": "Thick, creamy, smooth porridge — soft and spoonable like rich oatmeal, glossy with ghee on top; NEVER crispy, fried, or crusted",
